commands
~~~~~~~~~~~
1 - halp screen
2 - playlist screen
3 - browse
4 - browse by tag
5 - filter
6 - ?????

* all screens
    > - next song in playlist
    < - previous song in playlist

* playlist screen
    enter - play highlighted item
    p - pause
    s - stop
    j - up
    k - down
    i - more info

